meta {
  name: 03 Ping Chat
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

post {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/v1/chat/completions
  body: json
  auth: bearer
}

headers {
  Content-Type: application/json
}

auth:bearer {
  token: {{apiKey}}
}

body:json {
  {
    "model": "hermes-agent",
    "messages": [
      { "role": "user", "content": "Reply with the single word 'pong' and nothing else." }
    ]
  }
}

docs {
  Minimal round-trip through the LLM provider to confirm the chat path works end-to-end (gateway -> provider -> response). If this returns `pong`, the HERMES_INFERENCE_PROVIDER / OPENROUTER_API_KEY / HERMES_DEFAULT_MODEL chain is healthy.
}
